  "description": "Figure-eight at tangle 0.65, pulse 2.0 Hz — the two symmetric loops of the matrix act like a double helix: two interweaving signal paths that never quite occupy the same space. Square LFO on filter creates sharp rhythmic punctuation while the helix rotates. High aggression, wide spread.",
